    {
      "id": "1001899",
      "title": "",
      "description": "Weekend closure extension:\r\nRiders should note that the Green Line B Branch suspension will be extended to Copley during the weekend of April 25 \u2013 26.\r\n\r\nShuttle information:\r\nShuttle buses will not stop at Griggs Street, Allston Street, or Packard\u2019s Corner due to accessibility issues.\r\n\r\nAlternate service:\r\nOn April 22 \u2013 24 and April 27 \u2013 30, riders can also use free Route 57 bus service for alternate travel between Kenmore and Packard\u2019s Corner.\r\n\r\nAffected stops:\r\nKenmore\r\nBlandford Street\r\nBoston University East\r\nBoston University Central\r\nAmory Street\r\nBabcock Street\r\nPackard's Corner\r\nHarvard Avenue\r\nGriggs Street\r\nAllston Street\r\nWarren Street\r\nWashington Street\r\nSutherland Road\r\nChiswick Road\r\nChestnut Hill Avenue\r\nSouth Street\r\nBoston College",
      "severity": 7,
      "route_id": "unknown"
    },
    {
      "id": "1002019",
      "title": "",
      "description": "This is to accommodate track improvement work and the replacement of 14,000 railroad ties and is scheduled to complete mid-May, 2026.\r\n\r\nSingle-track operations will be in effect throughout this period so boarding areas may change.\r\n\r\nTemporarily Suspended Inbound Trains:\r\n\u2022\t126 (8:49am from Newburyport)\r\n\u2022\t1132 (10:53am from Beverly)\r\n\u2022\t46 (1:47pm from Rockport)\r\n\u2022\t1150 (3:23 from Beverly)\r\n\r\nTemporarily Suspended Outbound Trains:\r\n\u2022\t125 (8:35am to Newburyport)\r\n\u2022\t1129 (9:35am to Beverly)\r\n\u2022\t39 (12:05pm to Rockport)\r\n\u2022\t11:47am (2:05pm to Beverly)\r\n\r\n\r\n",
      "severity": 8,
